      "comment": "PINK MILK (1) was quickly out of the boxes with a slick early sectional clocking 23.50 with a 4.5 lengths win at this track over 411m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Expected to go well again. MISS POLLYWOOD (3) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 0.8 lengths away in second (23.42) behind Chad's Girl at this track. Leading player again. MISS RAVEN ROSE (7) turned in a plain performance last time when seventh at this track over 411m behind Chad's Girl (24.01) in a Grade 5. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Can figure in the finish. STEELY DAWN (8) took up a forward position and go the job done last time out. Right in the mix.",
